<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/db08e494ee4aab3eee23c7d963ec4a7f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="715" data-rawheight="505" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="715" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/db08e494ee4aab3eee23c7d963ec4a7f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="715" data-rawheight="505" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="715" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/db08e494ee4aab3eee23c7d963ec4a7f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/db08e494ee4aab3eee23c7d963ec4a7f_b.jpg"><br>夸你脸小呢。<br>君不见邱淑贞的脸就比张扑克牌大那么一点，一般人不得叼个ipad才有这效果？<br><br>以后叼个鸡腿就行了。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/240a54ab2a31b57bc5f3813f891be48b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="747" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/240a54ab2a31b57bc5f3813f891be48b_r.jpg">（示意图，这个是鸡排）</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="747" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/240a54ab2a31b57bc5f3813f891be48b_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/240a54ab2a31b57bc5f3813f891be48b_b.jpg">（示意图，这个是鸡排）<br><br><br>其实“比脸还大”原本就是台湾［豪大大鸡排］的广告词。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/9226894e94b4d387a706597961553deb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="776" data-rawheight="535" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="776" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/9226894e94b4d387a706597961553deb_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="776" data-rawheight="535" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="776" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/9226894e94b4d387a706597961553deb_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/9226894e94b4d387a706597961553deb_b.jpg"><br>我在台北那个士林夜市还吃过一次，什么味道忘了，反正确实挺大的。


